    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*I am looking for a publisher for my game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Contact: <a href=\"mailto:tttriet1997@gmail.com)\">tttriet1997@gmail.com)</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tu Tien Path is a 3D Xianxia Cultivation game, Fantasy Adventure RPG in UNREAL ENGINE 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free on your own path in the world. But you will be loneliness, and very consistency if you want to go to the highest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a part of a web novel, Q-Style with stylized object model and colors world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In mortal world, there are 5 levels in the Xianxia Cultivation Path that a normal human can achieve, of course you must spend blood and bone for it. Consistency and effort are not enough, luck will play a big part in it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Third-Person – Adventure RPG – Action – Shooting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world – Flight - Stealth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting – Building – Farming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classes – Hidden Objects – Life &amp; Immersive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/033b5fb871e327a55e3a690f785f4093.poster.avif?t=1768208745\" width=800 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/033b5fb871e327a55e3a690f785f4093.webm?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/033b5fb871e327a55e3a690f785f4093.mp4?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/fd9cf5294c89a76e9359163654a45844.poster.avif?t=1768208745\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/fd9cf5294c89a76e9359163654a45844.webm?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/fd9cf5294c89a76e9359163654a45844.mp4?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/4a8db4df6fc9eb1d4d10810a46a7cb57.poster.avif?t=1768208745\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/4a8db4df6fc9eb1d4d10810a46a7cb57.webm?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/4a8db4df6fc9eb1d4d10810a46a7cb57.mp4?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/b63e77bb9b239911fca11a1b75ec85c3.poster.avif?t=1768208745\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/b63e77bb9b239911fca11a1b75ec85c3.webm?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/b63e77bb9b239911fca11a1b75ec85c3.mp4?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/aae2cd03d6915f16da88b9501e60e24d.poster.avif?t=1768208745\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/aae2cd03d6915f16da88b9501e60e24d.webm?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/extras/aae2cd03d6915f16da88b9501e60e24d.mp4?t=1768208745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story or Setting:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Xianxia World, almost think Survival of the Strongest, but there is one, don’t want to kill, but live in peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For powerful Beasts, he tames. For extravagant people who want to kill him, he separates their body and soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of the whole story, he never kills, but it doesn’t mean he is a good person, there is still a darkness inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>System Requirements:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Window.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Benefits:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tu Tien Path contains philosophy of Buddhism, Confucianism and Taoism, self-help, mindset of a hard worker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Author word:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s just a game from a web-developer, it will go from bad to good as I will keep updating it for better new features or improvement in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I will read all the comments and try to make it better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your support will help me a lot, to live and develop the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please check out my game list:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Localization:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For now, just English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Youtube Chanel: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: </p>",
